             was indicted for <rs id="t18230219-14-off83" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18230219-14-off83" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230219-14-off83" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230219-14-cd84" type="crimeDate">25th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230219-14-off83 t18230219-14-cd84"></join>, three handkerchiefs, value 7 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18230219-14-victim163" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Bradley
                        <interp inst="t18230219-14-victim163" type="surname" value="Bradley"></interp>
